                    <> #0                 by field_exp_eq_zero, poly_lead_nonzero
                      q ' k
                    = f k                 by poly_sum_gen_coeff
                    = (p ' k) ** m

     Hence !k. q ' k = (p ' k) ** m       by claim
      Also !k. q ' k = p ' k              by q = p, [2]
      Thus !k. (p ' k) ** m = p ' k       by [1], [2]
