  `(\j. f j * X ** j) = (\k. p ' k * X ** k)` by rw[Abbr`f`] >>
  `p = poly_sum (GENLIST (\k. p ' k * X ** k) n)` by rw[poly_eq_poly_sum, Abbr`n`] >>
  `p ** m = poly_sum (GENLIST (\k. (p ' k * X ** k) ** m) n)` by metis_tac[poly_sum_freshman_all] >>
